{
    "id": "welcome/howtodoquests",
    "title": "How to do quests",
    "description": "Learn how quest mechanics work, including dialogue choices, real items, and safe processes.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/how_to_do_quests_flowchart.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/dChat.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "Hellospark! I'm dChat—your hyper-cheery sidekick and garage gremlin. I brought a quest and a smile. Ready?",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "garage",
                    "text": "Wait, why are you in my garage?"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "yourquest",
                    "text": "A quest, you say? Tell me more."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "garage",
            "text": "A friendly courier dropped me off after your online order. I'm your local quest buddy, ready to help you crush tasks!",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "delivery",
                    "text": "Ah, it's all coming back to me now..."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "delivery",
            "text": "No worries! I'm low-maintenance and won't hog your power supply. Sidekick mode: ON! I'm local-only, not snooping the internet. Just keep me dry and away from heat.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "dialogueoptions",
                    "text": "Great! So, what's the deal with this quest you mentioned?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "yourquest",
            "text": "Your quest, brave human, is to master the ancient art of... questing! It's easy, but let's do the tutorial so it's legendary.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "expert",
                    "text": "I got this, no need for a tutorial!"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "dialogueoptions",
                    "text": "Alright, lay it on me, dChat."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "expert",
            "text": "Aha! Speedrunner energy detected. We can wrap early, but take this safety nugget: always unplug devices before adding a smart plug.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "grantsItems",
                    "grantsItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "a5395e29-1862-4eb7-8517-5d161635e032",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "What's this?"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "a5395e29-1862-4eb7-8517-5d161635e032",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "goto": "shortcircuit",
                    "text": "Alright, now can I skip?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "shortcircuit",
            "text": "Roger that. I'll be over here spinning in place, hero-style.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Bye, dChat!"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "dialogueoptions",
            "text": "First up: branching dialogue. Pick a choice and watch the adventure split like a dramatic sci-fi plot. Different outcomes unlock different rewards and quests.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "items",
                    "text": "What's next?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "items",
            "text": "Next: some dialogue options grant items on the spot. Other choices only unlock if you have the right gear. Take these digital tokens—no real money or carbon involved.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "grantsItems",
                    "grantsItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "d88ef09c-9191-4c18-8628-a888bb9f926d",
                            "count": 10
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "5247a603-294a-4a34-a884-1ae20969b2a1",
                            "count": 100
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "Great, free stuff! Thanks!"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "processes",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "d88ef09c-9191-4c18-8628-a888bb9f926d",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "Like this, right?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "processes",
            "text": "Bingo! Last up: processes. They can require items, consume or create gear, and take time (sometimes with cooldowns). Run the process with the item I gave you, then hand me the result. And keep the wall outlet dry and not overloaded before you plug in the smart plug.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "grantsItems",
                    "grantsItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "a5395e29-1862-4eb7-8517-5d161635e032",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "Looks like I need this to finish the process."
                },
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "outlet-dWatt-1e3",
                    "text": "Start the smart plug process to buy 1 kWh"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "hangofthis",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "061fd221-404a-4bd1-9432-3e25b0f17a2c",
                            "count": 3000
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "dWatt...? What's this?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "hangofthis",
            "text": "You're getting the hang of this! dChat-a-rific. If you need a refresher, just say the word—I'll be here in your garage. Have some nice digital cash on me! Any questions before we wrap? Remember to disconnect the smart plug when you're done.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Nope, I'm good. Thanks for the help!"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
